short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: TabSync - Tabs Syncing across browsers and platforms

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: TabSync is your digital sidekick for keeping your browsing sessions in sync. No more scrambling to find that important tab on a different device! With TabSync, your open tabs follow you, like a loyal puppy, across all your browsers and platforms
